    Article('1987', '12', 'Digital and Vector Baseband Circuits for a Vector Signal Generator', 'By using a vector modulator instead of conventional amplitude and frequency modulators, the HP 8780A has the ability to generate complex digital and vector modulations. The baseband system is vastly different from those found in conventional signal generators. This system also provides the instrument with some special features', ['Chung Y. Lau'], '39-44', '', ''),
