    Article('1975', '5', 'A Precision Spectrum Analyzer for the 10-Hz-to-13-MHz Range', 'Adaptable to automatic systems or bench use, a new spectrum analyzer has measurement resolution of 0.01 dB, pass-bands as narrow as 3 Hz, and a dynamic range of 70 dB', ['Jerry W. Daniels', 'Robert L. Atchley'], '18-24', '', ''),
